data.description: This incredible home features an open kitchen, dining, and living area that is perfect for entertaining. It has granite countertops in the kitchen and bathrooms, a pantry, master closet, and laundry room. Vinyl plank flooring throughout, except for 2 bedrooms which are carpet. An amazing gated community… where beyond the amenities (lake views, golf course, restaurant, boating, fishing, swimming, playground, tennis, pickleball, meeting space, and lodging for guests), there is a lifestyle available for everyone. Don’t be surprised if you are greeted by an abundance of wildlife like deer and wild turkeys as you drive to your destination. Visit www.whitebluffpoa.com for HOA info and pictures of the amenities.
